description: Kasukarp`s Magikarp (Shinegoldie) is a Shiny Magikarp and was the winner of the tenth annual Magikarp high jump competition. Because Goh`s Giant Magikarp didn`t return to the field which was necessary for the successful completion of a jump, the judges ruled that Kasukarp`s Magikarp (Shinegoldie) was the winner.
name: Koiking (Kasuking)
